A 26-year-old house wife identified as Ummi Garba has been allegedly gang-raped and slaughtered by unknown persons in Jigawa State. A resident told Daily Post that the incident happened on Wednesday night at Warwadi quarters in Hadejia town. He said the incident occurred when the unknown criminals took advantage of her husband’s absence, sneaked into the house, raped and butchered her. -Advertisement- Police spokesman, ASP Lawan Shiisu Adam who confirmed the incident said, “on 01/06/2022 at about 1815hrs, when unknown persons trespassed into the compound of a 26-year-old house wife identified as Ummi Garba at Warwadi Quarters Hadejia, Local Government and used sharp object to slit her throat.” Shiisu said a team of policemen rushed to the scene after receiving the information and the victim was rushed to the General Hospital Hadejia for treatment. He said the victim died while receiving treatment and was confirmed dead by a medical doctor. The police spokesman however said the case was under investigation.